{"tid":2093051,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"下周五起59地區入境英格蘭毋須隔離　包活港澳台","createTime":"2020-07-03T14:55:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-04T03:38:37.000Z","uid":81228,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"03168d8d29cbea4567551de01047893b197bec7e","tid":2093051,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T14:55:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/aeanews/20200703/photo/bkn-20200703180432983-0703_00912_001_01b.jpg?20200703224756\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Faeanews%2F20200703%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20200703180432983-0703_00912_001_01b.jpg%3F20200703224756&h=968bc51b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n英格蘭將解除對部分地區的入境自我隔離規定。圖為倫敦希思路機場。（Getty Images圖片）<br />\n<br />\n隨着部分地區的新冠肺炎疫情紓緩，英國政府周五（3日）公布，下周五（10日）起解除來自59個國家及地區的入境英格蘭人士，需要自我隔離14日的規定，當中包括香港、澳門及台灣。另外，英國政府周六（4日）將會公布解除多國的旅遊警示，意味民眾將可以前往旅遊。<br />\n<br />\n運輸大臣夏博思受訪時指，連同英國海外屬地，將有約60個國家及地區獲解禁，但美國不會列入解禁名單。他指，會以紅黃綠三色，區分疫情傳播風險，其中法國、德國、意大利及西班牙等，會列入黃色級別，彼此會有互不隔離檢疫的安排，至於疫情仍然嚴峻的美國，就會列在紅色級別，來自美國的旅客仍需隔離14日。<br />\n<br />\n在野工黨黨魁施紀賢周五稱，將來調查首相約翰遜處理疫情失當是無可避免。另外，英國政府雖然要求國民避免非必要外遊，但約翰遜的父親卻很可能經保加利亞前往希臘，夏博思強調他有權這樣做。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/aeanews/20200703/bkn-20200703180432983-0703_00912_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Faeanews%2F20200703%2Fbkn-20200703180432983-0703_00912_001.html&d=C%2Fe7%2FQel5OtnIpuNpUi2IP5uq9964iqXyfozsjiZLe8%3D&h=20bbcd5b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/aeanews/20200703/bkn-20200703180432983-0703_00912_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"a0583a2e123280f1b99511bc9c53d08bc2c58d75","tid":2093051,"uid":134323,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T14:56:21.000Z","msg":"移民得<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f3593b3948555aaca84f073807f1b04259eea4f","tid":2093051,"uid":284855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T14:58:50.000Z","msg":"門已開"},{"pid":"e424387b8b7504733cead0010a00b575a93918d3","tid":2093051,"uid":62305,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T14:59:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26a3e8dd0b5ab8ea80184410571bb88a12f56134","tid":2093051,"uid":10094,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T15:01:12.000Z","msg":"動身了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 呢幾個星期走得"},{"pid":"73e161b778cbcd2ea7f7d3ff5af349531e9860b0","tid":2093051,"uid":89517,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T15:05:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0617ec915b44cc5e60198a450f3a4a56e67ef1a2","tid":2093051,"uid":111253,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T03:19:39.000Z","msg":"但返香港都要強制14日手帶"},{"pid":"b9831a986b4602aac93ad8cf3d59246157805cf0","tid":2093051,"uid":59920,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"0617ec915b44cc5e60198a450f3a4a56e67ef1a2","tid":2093051,"uid":111253,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T03:19:39.000Z","msg":"但返香港都要強制14日手帶"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T03:23:16.000Z","msg":"住5年，仲返香港？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f4d5a2a77e5460edb41c3772c5740a1b117d0df","tid":2093051,"uid":278219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T03:38:37.000Z","msg":"//在野工黨黨魁施紀賢周五稱，將來調查首相約翰遜處理疫情失當是無可避免。//<br />\n所以BJ家下咁強烈反共就係想補獲?"}]}